sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Producer
    participant B as Broker进程
    participant C as OS Page Cache
    participant D as 磁盘

    P->>B: Send(E1002)
    B->>C: 写入页缓存
    B-->>P: 返回成功
    Note over P: Producer认为发送完成
    B--xD: 刷盘前整机掉电
    Note over C: 页缓存丢失
    B->>D: 重启并恢复CommitLog
    Note over B,D: E1002可能不存在
